Pool

public Pool(java.lang.String name,
            double volumeLitres,
            double temperatureCelsius,
            double pH,
            double nutrientCoefficient)
Constructor for objects of class Pool. Note that the identification number is set automatically.

Parameters:
name - the Pool's name, a String
volumeLitres - a double representing the Pool's volume in litres
temperatureCelsius - a double representing the Pool's temperature. Must be in the range [MINIMUM_TEMPERATURE, MAXIMUM_TEMPERATURE] else set to default.
pH - a double representing the Pool's pH. Must be in the range [MINIMUM_PH, MAXIMUM_PH] else set to default.
nutrientCoefficient - a double representing the Pool's nutrientCoefficient. Must be in the range [MINIMUM_NUTRIENT_COEFFICIENT, MAXIMUM_NUTRIENT_COEFFICIENT] else set to default.
